---
title: Feta-Topped Avocado Toasts with Egg plus Cucumber Tomato Salad
description: For this colorful 15-minute riff on avocado toast, you’ll add sour cream to guacamole for a creamy sourdough topper. Next you’ll pile on a crisp, juicy cucumber and tomato salad, sprinkle with salty feta, then add the crowning glory: a perfectly poached egg. That’s just about the luckiest bread we can imagine.
